{"tid":1550704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到哩場運動瓶頸位","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:13:04.000Z","uid":113155,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e83437ccdccb89561d6a67565a64d66345213fe3","tid":1550704,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，98一定要出！唔出之前努力白費晒！</span></span><br />\n正題：<br />\n面對黑警光明正大濫捕濫權，巿民無計可施，又不敢博命，只能望住手足一個一個咁被捕。<br />\n咁多人自殺，我估哩個係其中一個原因。<br />\n<br />\n91當日，朋友親身經歷：<br />\n當天好多人，多數係和理非，和理非未見到黑警，淨係聽到full gear手足話行快啲，就開始兵慌馬亂，個個好驚咁走，完全冇諗過走太快，前線就變咗condom!<br />\n其實唔洗驚，人多嗰陣，我哋係狗幾倍人數，一有人被捉住咗就湧上去救人，而唔係見到狗就驚到震晒！<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，冇一場革命係和平！<br />\n勇武喺給哩次進化好大，和理非，求下你哋唔好再停滯不前，將重擔完全放喺勇武身上。<br />\n勇武人數冇你哋想象中咁多，仲要捉咗好大批，傷咗好大批！勇武冇人啦，和理非靠自己啦唔該！<br />\n人少嗰陣，你見到狗驚要走，冇人怪你。<br />\n但應承我，人多嗰陣，唔好再驚，保護番勇武，唔好人話散就散，當有成十幾萬人，黑警可以點捉？<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖其實好成功，如果你而家驚，遲啲有排你驚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3w1Ha6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3w1Ha6w.jpg&h=63126335&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0h5T2dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0h5T2dd.jpg&h=d75d3a01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jo4Q4rA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJo4Q4rA.jpg&h=1bd69224&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0X7ndg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0X7ndg.jpg&h=13a2bb7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umZ9Ayg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumZ9Ayg.jpg&h=0090a496&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5rjXMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5rjXMC.jpg&h=9eb3e80c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhcvjZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhhcvjZY.jpg&h=9c41bd00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd008d7c59dc955b8a31ea97614a6a869bb1fca8","tid":1550704,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24f92df3d0330843b34a3a97a3b8dced2d385480","tid":1550704,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n想叫和理非清醒啲"},{"pid":"4010033264c35b25fc769fe7f5478936aec61d67","tid":1550704,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"我哋一直靠嘅係人數，唔好再怯，怯就要怯一世架啦"},{"pid":"07fccde2b7f06bf72cc6592a946d1c5e3dd5a27f","tid":1550704,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e5640fab72f3345506ca72f547e5fc7a363298f","tid":1550704,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57945a0dcb75491cd8ebe3799c376d536a61bdfc","tid":1550704,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"716c22511f8c6530c0446258994e6a5f8f8153d